snippet.title: Astrid - concept demo now on G.Round! | Trailer
snippet.description:
We're live on G.Round!

Astrid can’t remember the last years of her life. Plagued by visions of a strange mansion, she embarks on a journey to recover her lost past. Now it is up to you to save her memories in an interactive film combining decision-based and 3D gameplay.

Leave us your feedback on GRound and follow us to stay up to date!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/trappedPredator
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TrappedPredator
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/trappedpredator
